children.text:
This keyboard application collects data from its distribution of emoji, sticker, and gif assets so we can learn about the popularity of our content and continue to provide our fans with fun and engaging creative content to share in their communications.

 We also collect information about general user behavior within the application in order to improve the user experience we've built for our fans.

 This data is analyzed internally, and personal information is not shared with outside advertisers for their own use. We do not store personal information and never track anything that is typed in your standard keyboard.
